    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"# Event Extraction System\\n\",\"**NLP Project 30 of 100** — Identify who did what, when, and where from news text.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import spacy, re, subprocess, sys\\ntry: nlp = spacy.load('en_core_web_sm')\\nexcept:\\n    subprocess.check_call([sys.executable,'-m','spacy','download','en_core_web_sm'])\\n    nlp = spacy.load('en_core_web_sm')\\nprint('Loaded.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"def extract_events(text):\\n    doc = nlp(text)\\n    events = []\\n    who = [e.text for e in doc.ents if e.label_ in ('PERSON','ORG')]\\n    where = [e.text for e in doc.ents if e.label_ in ('GPE','LOC')]\\n    when = [e.text for e in doc.ents if e.label_ in ('DATE','TIME')]\\n    # Extract main verb (action)\\n    actions = [t.lemma_ for t in doc if t.pos_ == 'VERB' and t.dep_ in ('ROOT','ccomp')]\\n    return {'who': who, 'what': actions, 'where': where, 'when': when}\\n\\ntexts = [\\n    'Apple announced new AI features in Cupertino on Monday.',\\n    'President Biden signed the infrastructure bill in Washington on November 15, 2025.',\\n    'Google acquired DeepMind in London in 2014 for $500 million.',\\n    'Thousands of people protested in Paris yesterday against the new policy.',\\n]\\n\\nfor text in texts:\\n    event = extract_events(text)\\n    print(f'Text: {text}')\\n    for k, v in event.items(): print(f'  {k:6s}: {v}')\\n    print()\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Summary\\n\",\"- **Event extraction uses NER + dependency parsing** to identify event components.\\n\",\"- **Who/What/When/Where framework** provides structured event representation.\\n\",\"- **For production, use event detection models** trained on ACE/ERE datasets.\"]}\n",
    " ],\n",
